    "By doing so, it is possible to mitigate the side effects AI may have on our society and environment while simultaneously enhancing its performance and efficiency.",
    "Case Studies Analysis.",
    "Over recent years, advertising recommendation systems employing Artificial Intelligence (AI) technology have significantly expanded by offering personalized advertisements based on the analysis of users' online behavior patterns.",
    "These systems have evolved with a subgoal of delivering tailored advertisements to enhance the user experience.",
    "However, some systems tend to excessively utilize users' personal information, leading to privacy infringement issues during the ad recommendation process."
